Package: CaBehavKit
Type: Package
Title: A Toolkit for Analyzing Neuronal Activity and Behavioral Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gao Yuxin
Maintainer: Gao Yuxin<2262457139@qq.com >
Description: The CaBehavKit package provides tools for the analysis of neuronal activity and
behavior data, focusing on calcium imaging and behavioral data integration. It includes functions for preprocessing data, performing neuronal activity analysis, aligning neural and behavioral data, and generating visualizations. The package is designed to support research in neurobiology, particularly in studying the relationship between neuronal activity and behavior.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, tidyr, data.table, magrittr
Suggests: testthat, knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
